channel.title: Hey, need some help with my god swords?
channel.description:
Hey, 1st of thank for taking the time to look at my topic.
Ok, well im having a little trouble with the god swords on my server, im using a deltascape soure. A week or two ago, i posted a topic about shop problems, and after i got all that sorted out, all the god swords on my server lost all of there stats, and show up as a non-existing item in the second trade screen.
I have tried reverting to backup shops, but its still doesn't work?
Little confused on why this happened, any help is highly appreciated. But please, no flaming. MSN: redeyeballs38@yahoo.com
